{"tid":1583854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"抒發 普通和理非嘅心態","createTime":"2019-09-20T23:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T23:50:44.000Z","uid":10691,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8913ffe86ec46fdac9b662a38198c7467979866b","tid":1583854,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T23:42:14.000Z","msg":"由六月一路抗爭到而家<br />\n三個月 累係正常 <br />\n想有時星期六日 做番港豬係人之常情<br />\n但希望你地 都要記得 你玩樂緊 休息緊嘅同時<br />\n好多義士可能係被捕緊 or 俾人打緊<br />\n希望大家仍然要保持憤怒<br />\n好多不公係仍然發生緊<br />\n或者你可以暫時出黎 但希望你仍然做網上嘅文宣<br />\n呢件事已經係最簡單 最唔辛苦<br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家 十月一日 就算有咩事都放底先(當然死人冧樓另計)<br />\n都100000000000% 要出黎 再一次 200萬人<br />\n要俾全世界知道我地嘅決心 <br />\n香港人對不公 係唔可以習慣"},{"pid":"b7c06a294ce8d373617d734c4ba2feec1cb523c7","tid":1583854,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T23:42:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"91598ecf1d04ef918be36a5ec77296d8d6a95956","tid":1583854,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T23:42:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7ace2d36e179da2bf604e792388433cb994b0cb","tid":1583854,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T23:42:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"784770dd0d97d1a476852281571fda563f5bac38","tid":1583854,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T23:47:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e81abd25abb4c4199f5d9830daa48d84be87575","tid":1583854,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T23:50:44.000Z","msg":"推"}]}